sequenceDiagram
accTitle: Mermaid rect nesting and fragments
accDescr {
Demonstrates nested Mermaid rect highlights and their interaction with structural fragments.
From the project root, regenerate this Mermaid transform and SVG with:
node sequencer.js --mermaid -i test/mermaid-features/15-rect-nesting-and-fragments/input.mmd -o -f -t test/mermaid-features/15-rect-nesting-and-fragments
}
participant Caller
participant Service
participant DB
participant Cache
participant Audit
rect rgba(255, 230, 200, 0.5)
  Service->>DB: Outer same-start write [Mermaid: Service->>DB: Outer same-start write]
  rect rgba(255, 190, 190, 0.5)
    Service->>Cache: Inner same-start warm [Mermaid: Service->>Cache: Inner same-start warm]
  end
  opt Optional audit branch rgb(220, 240, 0)
    Service->>Audit: Audit within rect [Mermaid: Service->>Audit: Audit within rect]
  end
end
opt Outer optional branch
  rect rgb(220, 240, 255)
    DB->>Audit: Rect inside fragment [Mermaid: DB->>Audit: Rect inside fragment]
  end
end
rect rgba(220, 255, 220, 0.6)
  Service->>Audit: Outer different-start anchor [Mermaid: Service->>Audit: Outer different-start anchor]
  rect rgba(200, 235, 255, 0.6)
    DB->>Audit: Inner different-start anchor [Mermaid: DB->>Audit: Inner different-start anchor]
  end
end
